name: DigitalOffset
description:
All images above are first try, not cherry picked (batch 4, same prompt, model=test). v0.2 also first try (batch 4, model=DigitalOffset2_1).

A merge of Perfect World, DalcefoV3Painting (not the 2nd version, it doesn't work so good for me) and Noise Offset for True Darkness trained on ~1000 Nixeu/WLOP images.

Loving the effect whole picture noise offset can bring. Much to come I believe.

Upscaled with latent 2x 35 Steps, 768x768 default, DPM++ SDE 50 Steps

modelVersions.name: v.0.2
modelVersions.description:
Better Faces, much punchier Colours and more intricate details.

Added keywords: wlop, nixeu

Trained v.0.1 with ~1000 Nixeu/WLOP Images (with noise offset). Merged with v.0.1 (with DalcefoV3Painting changed to DalcefoV3Painting_3rd). Baked MSE VAE from stablediffusion.
